# Quick Start

This guide gets a fresh checkout of **{{ project_name }}** ready for local development.

## Install Dependencies

```bash
uv sync --dev
```

## Run the Example

```python
from {{ package_name }} import greet

print(greet("World"))
```

## Run the Quality Checks

```bash
uv run ruff check .
uv run pyright
{% if include_tests -%}
uv run pytest --cov=src
{% endif -%}
```